Package: rems2aquachem
Type: Package
Title: Download from rems and export data in format for AquaChem
Version: 0.2.0
Author: Steffi LaZerte
Maintainer: Steffi LaZerte <steffi@steffi.ca>
Description: Use bcgov package 'rems' to download data for specific EMS ids. 
    Convert data to format for easy importing into AquaChem. ShinyApp included 
    to provide user-friendly GUI.
License: file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
